| 9 |  | #P_funimaexg | |- ( ( Fun F /\ A e. B ) -> ( F " A ) e. _V ) |

| 16 | 10, 15 | #P_syldan | |- ( ( F Fn A /\ A e. B ) -> ran F e. _V ) |

| 18 | 7, 16, 17 | #P_syl2anc | |- ( ( F Fn A /\ A e. B ) -> ( dom F X. ran F ) e. _V ) |
| 19 |  | #P_ssexg | |- ( ( F C_ ( dom F X. ran F ) /\ ( dom F X. ran F ) e. _V ) -> F e. _V ) |

 Alternate proof of ~ fnex , derived using the Axiom of Replacement in the form of ~ funimaexg .  This version uses ~ ax-pow and ~ ax-un , whereas ~ fnex does not.  (Contributed by NM, 14-Aug-1994.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)  (New usage is discouraged.)
